<number box="[220,233,1924,1948]" pageId="5" pageNumber="28" value="2.0">2</number>
with end claw G 
<number box="[431,445,1924,1948]" pageId="5" pageNumber="28" value="2.0">2</number>
very wide and stout in the female, and with a series of rounded teeth in the distal 
<number box="[1393,1408,1924,1948]" pageId="5" pageNumber="28" value="2.0">2</number>
/ 
<number box="[1419,1432,1924,1948]" pageId="5" pageNumber="28" value="3.0">3</number>
